title: Camco 90-Degree Hose Elbow with Easy Grip Connector | Perfect for RV Water hookups and Residential Outdoor faucets | 2-Pack | (22507)
description: Camco's 90-Degree Hose Elbow helps eliminate strain on your water hose connection and helps stop hose kinking. It is ideal for RV water hookups, residential outdoor faucets and washing machine hookups. This durable, solid brass elbow fits standard water hose connections. It features a swiveling easy grip connector for simple installation and removal. CSA lead-free content certified to NSF/ANSI 372 and compliant with all federal and state level lead-free laws. 2-Pack.
